```plantuml
@startuml BoraxTheClean_DevelopmentMachine
actor Developer
participant GitHubActions
participant AWS_CLI
participant CloudFormation
participant IAM
participant EC2
participant CloudWatch

Developer -> GitHubActions: Triggers workflow (push/PR)
GitHubActions -> AWS_CLI: Configure AWS credentials
AWS_CLI -> IAM: Assume role (security check)
IAM --> AWS_CLI: Temporary credentials
AWS_CLI -> CloudFormation: Deploy stack (template.yaml)
CloudFormation -> IAM: Create/verify IAM role
CloudFormation -> EC2: Launch instance with security group
CloudFormation -> CloudWatch: Create inactivity alarm
CloudWatch --> EC2: Monitor CPU utilization
EC2 --> CloudWatch: Metrics
alt Inactivity detected
    CloudWatch -> EC2: Stop instance
end
@enduml
```